name: Porsche Panamera
description: The Porsche Panamera is a mid/full-sized luxury car (E-segment in Europe) manufactured by the German automobile manufacturer Porsche. It is front-engined and has a rear-wheel-drive layout, with all-wheel drive versions also available.
